'''Castel Primary School''' is located in [[Castel, Guernsey|Castel]] in [[Guernsey]] in the [[Channel Islands]]. It is a mixed gender [[States of Guernsey|States]] school for children up to the age of eleven. The girls' school was built in 1898 and was constructed with pink granite, and the boys' school was built in 1909 and was constructed with blue granite.

